<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/235173-could-the-murder-of-a-clone-really-be">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Could the murder of a clone really be considered suicide in the real legal world? This point intrigued me and has been on my mind continually since reading this story. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
